SAP Senior Consultant - PT ECCO Indonesia
SAP Senior Consultant  -
SAP Senior Consultant
Responsibilities
Assist SAP Development area as Senior Consultant and taking responsibilities in co-assisting ECCO transforming and innovate its business into concept and solution to achieve business objectives. Responsibilities:1. Considerable knowledge and understanding of SAP application based solutions with proficiency in SAP PP Module, secondary MM module2. Considerable experience consulting, designing, implementing and contributing as a functional team member.3. Demonstrated experience identifying and addressing business requirements: engage with business to clarify and discuss business context and requirements, translate business requirement into different relevant scenarios, and making recommendation.4. Execute task independently and engage with peers on aligning the design and execution tasks within the competence area of senior consultancy responsibilities.5. Ensure Successful of IT Change Management including Testing, Quality assurance, documentation, knowledge sharing and handover sustainable operation and supports. Requirements:• Minimum Bachelor Degree (S1) with Major in Computer Science/Information Technology, Industrial Engineering, or equivalent.• With experience in the position as SAP Consultant with at least 3 full life-cycle implementation with minimum 5 years’ experience.• Must have a good knowledge in SAP module (ex: Configuration/Customizing ) and good communication with business people• Ability to define business requirement/blueprint.• Have experience within an international and/or multinational fast paced environment would be an advantage• Proven ability to work creatively and analytically in a problem-solving environment• Proven success in contributing to a team-oriented environment.• Able to work under pressure.• Good English language communication skill is a must.• Flexible and service minded with excellent collaborative skills.• Business travelling abroad will be required depends on the project allocation.• Applicants must be willing to work in Sidoarjo.• Full-Time position(s) available.
